T02TD3241E:10a-1: badzra shrim kh'a la s'a dha nam /
T02TD3241E:10a-3: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3241E:10a-4: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3241E:10a-5: sngar bshad pa'i cho ga'i rim pas /
T02TD3241E:10a-6: snying gar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la yi ge h'um ljang gu'i ye shes nges par rdzogs pa las rdo rje lcags sgrog ma zhal gsum phyag drug ma ste /
T02TD3241E:10a-7: mthing nag dang dkar po ni g-yas pa dang cig shos kyi zhal lo //
T02TD3241E:10b-0: spyan gsum ma rdo rje dang rdo rje dang rdo rje lcags thag dang mda' dang ldan pa ni g-yas pa'i phyag @10b gsum mo //
T02TD3241E:10b-1: sdigs mdzub dang zhags pa dang /
T02TD3241E:10b-2: gzhu dang ldan pa ni g-yon pa'i phyag gsum mo //
T02TD3241E:10b-4: zhal cung zad bzhad pa dang ldan pa /
T02TD3241E:10b-5: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3241E:10b-6: ma rungs pa'i sems can gtan nas 'joms par mdzad par bdag nyid bsgoms la phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste /
T02TD3241E:10b-7: lag pa gnyis so sor rdo rje khu tshur du byas la mthe'u chung gnyis dang mdzub mo gnyis kyang lcags thag gi rnam par mdun par bya ba'o //
T02TD3241E:10b-8: aom badzra shrim kha le h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3241E:10b-9: zhes bya ba ni bzlas pa'i sngags so //
T02TD3241E:10b-10: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma'i sgrub thabs so /
T02TD3241E:10b-12: // / ma la ba'i zhal snga nas dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
